<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF207-900-714  </DOCNO><DOCID>07 900 714.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>PC Week  Nov 20 1989 v6 n46 p54(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Ziff-Davis Publishing Co. 1989.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>XTree revamps utility line across three user levels. (XTreePro,XTreePro Gold) (product announcement)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Smith, Gina.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Executive Systems Inc. XTree Co. (product introduction).andO;Product:   XTree (File management software) (product enhancement)Xtree Pro (Utility program) (product enhancement)XTreePro Gold (File management software) (product introduction).andO;Topic:     Utility ProgramsEnhancementsProduct Introduction.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>By Gina SmithandM;In an attempt to more clearly address the needs of its beginning,intermediate and advanced users, XTree Co. last week announced it hasshuffled features and prices for its two existing utilities and has added athird, higher-end package to its lineup.andM;For inexperienced users, the firm's low-end XTree entry now serves as asimple DOS shell that allows users to perform rudimentary file- anddirectory-management tasks without having to access the DOS prompt.andM;In recasting the software, XTree also has slashed the package's price to $69from $129.andM;The intermediate offering, XTreePro, adds to the first package by including abuilt-in text editor and faster log-on speed.andM;The midlevel XTree offering now carries an $89 price tag, down from $129,according to officials from the San Luis Obispo, Calif., firm.andM;On the high end, the firm unveiled a new program, XTreePro Gold, which offersthe power of XTreePro plus search and retrieval functions similar to thosefound in Lotus Development Corp.'s Magellan, according to company officials.andM;The program also sports an applications- launching feature that allows usersto start other programs without having to exit XtreePro Gold.andM;XTreePro Gold allows users to view and manipulate directory trees that cancontain up to 13,000 files located on as many as 26 hard or floppy disks, theofficials said.andP;  It also includes &quot;prune and graft&quot; capabilities, allowingusers to graphically relocate whole sections of a directory tree, they added.andM;XTreePro Gold is available now for $129.andM;XTree Co., a division of Executive Systems Inc., can be reached at (805)541-0604.andO;</TEXT></DOC>